spec_data.Name: perl-File-Find-Rule
spec_data.Description:
File::Find::Rule is a friendlier interface to File::Find.  It allows
you to build rules which specify the desired files and directories.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 11:33:44 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Perl module implementing an alternative interface to File::Find
